title: Chessbase Mega Database 2014 [German English]
description:
===============================================
 Chessbase Mega Database 2014 [German English] 
===============================================

A large reference chess database from Chessbase, in standard .cbh format

Languages: German, English
Size: compressed 0.97 GB, installed 3.7+ GB

-5,792,434 chess games played between 1475 and mid-November 2013
-Chess games only, playerbase with photos not included
-67,500 games annotated by top players
-ECO opening classifications
-100,000+ keys to positions, players, tournaments, middlegame themes, endgames

Directions:
(1) Run SetupMega2014.exe to install
(2) Open .cbh file with Chessbase or a Fritz GUI (Junior, Hiarcs, Shredder...) 

PLEASE HELP SEED!
